albums.title: O'Farrel and Polk
albums.subtitle: A Post-Pandemic Corner
albums.description: I'm on Polk street, between O'Farrel and Ellis. Scenes of a shuttered San Francisco. Broken people on the street, doing fentanyl. The flotsam and jetsam of a cultural moment.
